#meteorology isn't just on the local news! New work in @NatureClimate links increase in human-caused emissions in Tibetan Plateau to the loss of #Arctic #seaice. Less ice->weaker polar winds->less mountain snow->stronger warmer winds bringing emissions. https://t.co/TccSz8Wn39 https://t.co/JsTlelosi1
